                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, E</hi> 85). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read</hi>:</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185608180132"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Clerkenwell Sessions, Samuel Hill, Convicted Jan.</hi> 1856, <hi rend="italic">of stealing</hi> 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. <hi rend="italic">from the person—
Confined six months</hi>)—I had him in custody, and was pre<lb></lb>sent at the trial—Hill is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HILL</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
GUILTY</hi>. Aged 38. <hi rend="italic">
